(20242, 'Halorange syrup 60 ml', 'هالورانج شراب 60 مل', '49', '75', 'Cod liver oil+vitamin e', 'Eimc > tetrapharm', 'Syrup', 'شراب', '', 'Multivitamins', '60 ml', 'Cod liver oil is predominantly manufactured, marketed, and used by the population at large as a general nutraceutical dietary supplement [A27154, A33159, L2872].
